  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>This exclusive tour takes you on a journey through some of the most important foodie cities of Italy, taking in their culinary delights and colourful histories. You’ll get to experience some of the best food and unmissable sites of Emilia Romagna, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/58d85ec0faa548b2ab580143fdc9b722" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/tuscany-umbria" title="Tuscany &amp; Umbria">Tuscany and Umbria</a><span> in an intimate environment with a passionate guide</span>.</p>
<div>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: </strong>26</p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/gastronomic-tour-of-central-italy#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/gastronomic-tour-of-central-italy#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/gastronomic-tour-of-central-italy#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/gastronomic-tour-of-central-italy#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/gastronomic-tour-of-central-italy#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
